      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.03333333507180214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "確かに言わなかったのは悪かったよ……\nでも本当に、決まったのは昨日のことなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry I couldn’t tell you earlier.\nBut it was only just decided yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.704575774544163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 7.431882190704345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "多分、それで話がなくなったら私たちが落ち込むって\n思ったんじゃないのかなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "He probably didn’t want to disappoint us‚\nin case it fell through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.831882190704343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……まあ、それは分からないでもないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I guess that sort of makes sense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.765215524037677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.26521552403768
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 20.665215524037677
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "無用なプレッシャーもかかるかもしれないですしね\nま、私には無縁ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ it would’ve placed unnecessary pressure on us.\nWell‚ the rest of you—not me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.66521552403768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 23.4954878171285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "デビューするということはVENUSプログラムにも\n登録されるということですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doesn’t our debut also mean that\nwe’ll be registered into the VENUS Program?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.728821150461833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.262154483795168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 30.52882115046187
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（VENUSプログラムはアイドルのランキング制度だ）\n（その中でも今現在上位にいるアイドルが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The VENUS Program is a ranking system for idols.）\n（And the idols currently at the top of the ranking are…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.72882115046184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 36.9364175717036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…The BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.9364175717036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 38.56975090503693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（どのグループも既にホールを満員にする力がある）\n（間違いなくトップアイドルだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Each group already possesses the ability to sell out any venue.）\n（They are the undisputed top idols.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.43641757170361,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "頑張らなくっちゃね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve got our work cut out for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.46975090503694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 46.18877580165864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "その前に、NEXT VENUSグランプリですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Starting with the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.18877580165864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 49.88877584934236
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "でも……出たくても出られない\n大会自体が行われていないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… we couldn’t participate even if we wanted to\nsince the competition currently isn’t being held.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.055442516009016,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 55.08877584934235
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 55.75544251600897
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリは）\n（三年前の麻奈の死をきっかけに休止が続いている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ever since Mana’s death three years ago‚）\n（the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix has been on hiatus.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.62210918267567,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（グランプリと麻奈の死には直接なんの関係もない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（There was no direct connection between the Grand Prix and Mana’s death.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.82172383467356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（でもグランプリのために麻奈が多忙を極めたことが）\n（事故の原因であるかのように書き立てられた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But the news headlines hinted at Mana’s busy schedule during the Grand Prix）\n（as the possible cause of her accident.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.38839059670765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 70.20755137602487
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "新人アイドルは受難の時代って言われていますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They say it’s a difficult time to be a new idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.20755137602487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあね、NEXT VENUSグランプリは\n新人アイドルが目立つのに、一番の舞台でしたもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ of course. The NEXT VENUS Grand Prix\nwas the ultimate stage for new idols to stand out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.80755132834116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_platform-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 81.40755132834116
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "今は、いきなりVENUSプログラムに登録されて\n一番下から頑張っていくしかないんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "These days‚ idols are immediately enrolled in the VENUS Program\nand have to work their way up from the bottom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.34088466167447,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_train-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5025.782004992195,
          "startTime": 90.36666666666666
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 89.34088466167448
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 89.34088466167448
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 89.5742179950078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（地方都市である星見市にもダンススタジオは存在する）\n（しかしレベルの高い指導は望めない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（There are dance studios in the regional city of Hoshimi‚）\n（but they don’t offer the highest level of training.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.40755132834116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（そこで三枝さんが過去の人脈を活かして）\n（東京のダンス講師を紹介してくれた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So Saegusa-san drew on his past contacts）\n（and arranged dance lessons for the girls in Tokyo.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.00755132834114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 102.41077125072475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらたちは、先に行ってるんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura and her group went first‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.41077125072476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 105.47403657436368
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、三枝さんと一緒に。でも今日は残念だけど\nみんなとは別のスタジオなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right‚ with Saegusa-san. Unfortunately‚ today‚\nyou’ll be taking lessons in different studios.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.74070324103036,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 111.8740365743637
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8740365743637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_04_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、俺もみんなを送ったら\n一度さくらたちのレッスンを見に行こうと思ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep. After I take all of you to your lesson‚\nI’m thinking of checking in on Sakura and the others.",
        "id": ""
